Document: RDPipelineColorBlendStateAttachment
Path: godot/classes/class_rdpipelinecolorblendstateattachment.rst
Summary: Describes the color blend state for a single render target attachment in a render pipeline.

Inherits: RefCounted

This class describes the color blend state for a single render target attachment in a render pipeline. It is used within RDPipelineColorBlendState.

Properties:
blend_mode (int): The blend mode to use. Possible values:
- BLEND_MODE_DISABLED (0): Blending is disabled.
- BLEND_MODE_ADD (1): Additive blending.
- BLEND_MODE_SUBTRACT (2): Subtractive blending.
- BLEND_MODE_MULTIPLY (3): Multiplicative blending.
- BLEND_MODE_MIN (4): Minimum blending.
- BLEND_MODE_MAX (5): Maximum blending.
- BLEND_MODE_ALPHA (6): Alpha blending. Default: BLEND_MODE_DISABLED.

blend_equation_rgb (int): The blend equation for RGB components. Possible values:
- BLEND_EQUATION_ADD (0): Adds the source and destination colors.
- BLEND_EQUATION_SUBTRACT (1): Subtracts the destination color from the source color.
- BLEND_EQUATION_REVERSE_SUBTRACT (2): Subtracts the source color from the destination color.
- BLEND_EQUATION_MIN (3): Takes the minimum of the source and destination colors.
- BLEND_EQUATION_MAX (4): Takes the maximum of the source and destination colors. Default: BLEND_EQUATION_ADD.

blend_equation_alpha (int): The blend equation for the alpha component. Possible values:
- BLEND_EQUATION_ADD (0): Adds the source and destination colors.
- BLEND_EQUATION_SUBTRACT (1): Subtracts the destination color from the source color.
- BLEND_EQUATION_REVERSE_SUBTRACT (2): Subtracts the source color from the destination color.
- BLEND_EQUATION_MIN (3): Takes the minimum of the source and destination colors.
- BLEND_EQUATION_MAX (4): Takes the maximum of the source and destination colors. Default: BLEND_EQUATION_ADD.

src_color_blend_factor (int): The source color blend factor. Possible values:
- BLEND_FACTOR_ZERO (0): Zero.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE (1): One.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_COLOR (2): Source color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_SRC_COLOR (3): One minus source color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_ALPHA (4): Source alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_SRC_ALPHA (5): One minus source alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_DST_ALPHA (6): Destination alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_DST_ALPHA (7): One minus destination alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_DST_COLOR (8): Destination color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_DST_COLOR (9): One minus destination color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_ALPHA_SATURATED (10): Source alpha saturated. Default: BLEND_FACTOR_ONE.

dst_color_blend_factor (int): The destination color blend factor. Possible values:
- BLEND_FACTOR_ZERO (0): Zero.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE (1): One.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_COLOR (2): Source color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_SRC_COLOR (3): One minus source color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_ALPHA (4): Source alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_SRC_ALPHA (5): One minus source alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_DST_ALPHA (6): Destination alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_DST_ALPHA (7): One minus destination alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_DST_COLOR (8): Destination color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_DST_COLOR (9): One minus destination color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_ALPHA_SATURATED (10): Source alpha saturated. Default: BLEND_FACTOR_ZERO.

src_alpha_blend_factor (int): The source alpha blend factor. Possible values:
- BLEND_FACTOR_ZERO (0): Zero.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE (1): One.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_COLOR (2): Source color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_SRC_COLOR (3): One minus source color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_ALPHA (4): Source alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_SRC_ALPHA (5): One minus source alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_DST_ALPHA (6): Destination alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_DST_ALPHA (7): One minus destination alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_DST_COLOR (8): Destination color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_DST_COLOR (9): One minus destination color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_ALPHA_SATURATED (10): Source alpha saturated. Default: BLEND_FACTOR_ONE.

dst_alpha_blend_factor (int): The destination alpha blend factor. Possible values:
- BLEND_FACTOR_ZERO (0): Zero.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE (1): One.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_COLOR (2): Source color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_SRC_COLOR (3): One minus source color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_ALPHA (4): Source alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_SRC_ALPHA (5): One minus source alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_DST_ALPHA (6): Destination alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_DST_ALPHA (7): One minus destination alpha.
- BLEND_FACTOR_DST_COLOR (8): Destination color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_ONE_MINUS_DST_COLOR (9): One minus destination color.
- BLEND_FACTOR_SRC_ALPHA_SATURATED (10): Source alpha saturated. Default: BLEND_FACTOR_ZERO.

color_write_enable (bool): Whether color writing is enabled for this attachment. Default: true.
